	<li>Enthusiasm, a desire to learn and an interest in people</li>
	<li>Good communication skills, both written and verbal</li>
	<li>Good organisation skills and attention to detail</li>
	<li>Keen business interest and an enquiring nature</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

